name: Honey, I Crashed into Trees (Tree Crash)
name_original: Honey, I Crashed into Trees (Tree Crash)
description:
'Honey, I Crashed into Trees'
oh my god, are you trying to save trees from being cut?

created for the "Ready Set Jam" game jam by Vimlark (@Vimlark)

Controls:

One button controls (Gamepad / Mouse / Keyboard)

  • Tap to change turn direction.
  • Hold to Speed Forward

- Space (Keyboard)

- A/B/X/Y Buttons (Gamepad)

-  Left Click (Mouse)
